## Grouping Related Actions

When multiple insights point to the same solution, create one comprehensive action:

### Multiple Insights:
1. "Users forget to save before navigating away"
2. "Lost work is top complaint in feedback"
3. "Users manually save excessively out of fear"

### Single Action:
```json
{
  "title": "Implement auto-save with visual indicator",
  "description": "Multiple research findings show users are anxious about losing work. Implement auto-save every 30 seconds with clear visual feedback showing save status. Include 'last saved' timestamp.",
  "sourceInsight": "insight-save-anxiety, insight-lost-work, insight-manual-save"
}
```

